{"tid":578360,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[CCCU]城大專上學院2017 簡介(4)","createTime":"2018-03-02T14:20:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T05:34:56.000Z","uid":165025,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f77e7cb4eb207d3f00eb6cbcbeade1a3dcca8a5f","tid":578360,"uid":165025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T14:20:24.000Z","msg":"簡介下CCCU<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">[u]常見問題 Q&amp;A</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>Q1. 點解要讀副學士？</strong></span><br />\nA: 為左入返UGC <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有人唔適合DSE，可能適合副學士。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">Q2. 點解要揀CCCU?</span></strong><br />\nA: 所謂「三大CC」之一（HKCC, HKUSPACE ，CCCU），知名度較高，73%升學率當中42%升返UGC，由城大＋出面第三方機構監察課程質有保證。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>Q3. 揀咩科會易升U？</strong></span><br />\nA. 本人認為無乜伏唔伏科 只有你岩唔岩讀<br />\n邊科升u率高都唔係重點<br />\n一來 升得高只係果年班人勁 係因為班人勁 所以果科升u率當年高<br />\n二來 高都可能無你份<br />\n重點你會唔會願意努力不懈咁去準備一個又一個既 assignments project test exam<br />\n當你願意咁做 邊間 咩科都升到U。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>Q4. CCCU 賣盤對新生有無影響？</strong></span><br />\nA: 聽聞今年可以用到CITY既野小左，但好似未出官方報告。（歡迎更正）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>Q5. CCCU有分九龍塘本部同九龍灣兩間，邊間好d?</strong></span><br />\nA: 兩間應有盡有，有靚Lecture theatre有電腦有printer有好導師有自修室有Wifi，只係揀科時要留意下果科係邊間讀就得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>Q6. 屋企窮但又想經Asso升返上UGC學位，點算？</strong></span><br />\nA: 學資處幫到你，家庭月入及資產唔過限額的話係會批Grant Loan比你埋學費讀，（視乎你窮成點，可能批你75%學費免還）唔洗還的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，仲會借生活費比你（要還）渡過呢兩年，所以比心機D。而屋企唔合資格但又唔夠錢讀既同學可以揀免入息審查貸款即Loan，呢個係要還錢。<br />\n學資處Grant Loan <a href=\"http://www.wfsfaa.gov.hk/sfo/tc/postsecondary/fasp/overview.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wfsfaa.gov.hk%2Fsfo%2Ftc%2Fpostsecondary%2Ffasp%2Foverview.htm&d=w%2BnmYi19TIX5nP1VBUj9gr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=6ed96ba9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.wfsfaa.gov.hk/sfo/tc/postsecondary/fasp/overview.htm</a> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>Q7. 咩叫大O中O細O( Camp) ?</strong></span><br />\nA: 我既定義係大O=城大學生會/學系搞既，中O就係指CCCU有d Society搞既聯科Ocamp，細O 係指一個學科自己幫新生搞，規模較細，亦通常較平，因為有心既師兄會盡量壓低價錢吸引新生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>Q8. 去唔去Ocamp好？</strong></span><br />\nA: 如果係under city搞既，你參加ocamp為左娛樂同識下人既話，我絕對建議。 但只求為groupmates就免了。因為你未必遇到同科，同科未必同班。當然，你報既ocamp都會得到讀書上既幫助，對你都係有好處。如果係只限asso參加既，強烈建議。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>Q9. 衍生問題: OCAMP會爛GPA? 曬時間?</strong></span><br />\n首先Ocamp都係用你幾日時間(onight+ocamp)，多數都係開學前搞既。<br />\n用你開學前既幾日其實係爛唔到你GPA。<br />\n再講，你開左學之後都唔只HEA幾日啦。<br />\n曬唔曬時間就睇你份人鍾唔鍾意社交同玩啦。<br />\n你覺得唔太夾既，可以唔出席CAMP後活動 。<br />\n唔夾到令你討厭既地步，玩緊CAMP走都奈你唔何。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>Q10. 開左學咁唔好彩遇到freerider咪爛GPA？</strong></span><br />\nA: group report、presentation，依兩份功課都有機會遇上freeriders。 <br />\n自己一個做晒都有可能。 <br />\n咁到底自己一個做晒影響係咪真係好大？ <br />\n都幾大，主要係令你私人時間小左好多，做既野唔會話好深，係曬你時間搵資料，打字，組織，排板。重點係，小左時間溫書。<br />\nfreeriders係對你gpa有影響，但爛既話就未必。始終以組去完成功課佔比重唔高(商科) 。<br />\n<br />\n參考資料來源：MHI27000H7巴打 LIHKGID：#11258 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/247811/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/247811/page/1</a><br />\n自己<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=SC&amp;message=6443010&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DSC%26message%3D6443010%26highlight_id%3D0%26page%3D1%26authorOnly%3DFalse&d=w%2BnmYi19TIX5nP1VBUj9gr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=4b275ae0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=SC&amp;message=6443010&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False</a><br />\n上面依個Post會更加詳細講解商科。"},{"pid":"230f3078b891f7c8c2eb08a699ae665b47df5338","tid":578360,"uid":165025,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T14:21:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>Q11. 英文唔好會唔會唔夠其他人競爭？</strong></span><br />\nA: Asso真係咩人都有，有DSE廿幾分衰中文既人，有讀過恆管／Asso／Ive既人，商科asso要dse拎幾多先讀到，唔會讀得好吃力? <br />\n我個人認為最好有3-4既中間或以上係最好 <br />\n最好寫野同閱讀能力較強 <br />\n一來你要睇大量notes 一個sem最小5科，當你每科十課都50份notes <br />\n二來你考試都要寫D 短既段落<br />\n如果英文grammar 錯到一個地步連理解都成問題 真係會影響你個分數 <br />\n所以最好寫野叻小小 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>Q12.Retake定係讀Asso好？</strong></span><br />\nA: 唔敢亂答，有人差一兩分有人差七分都話Retake，只可以話睇你鐘唔鐘意DSE果D考試同學習方式、科目同適唔適合讀，Retake唔代表你手上有上年個分再升分，係由0考起，有機會跌分，咁就一年。DSE一試定生死，Asso就有50%分數都係平時寫Assignment做Presentation拎既，考試範圍又會話埋比你知，提早準備，講學習氣氛一定係輕鬆D。不過Asso你讀唔上返UGC就無回頭路，只可以揀自資學士課程，亦唔建議雙修因為兩邊D課程都好花時間讀，二揀一啦最好。[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>Q13.聽聞有伏tutor/lecturer？</strong></span><br />\nLecture，如果不幸遇到個你認為教得唔好既老師，可以選擇SIT第2個老師既堂，如果第2個都係伏，咁就唯有自修，睇番參考書。 <br />\nTUTOR，好難避，部份比分嚴既，真係唯有硬食，自己做好D。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>Q14.拎好成績好難?</strong></span><br />\n先定義好成績為3.7或以上，我果班有25-30人。 <br />\nCgpa過3.7既應該有5-6個。 <br />\n首先要勤力先啦，有智慧而荒廢學業都高極有限。 <br />\n勤力之餘都要識得溫書，有時唔係溫得耐就係好 <br />\n最理想既當然係每星期清番果個星期教既野，唔識就問番老師(我自己都做唔到) <br />\n做唔到既，都認真對待mid term，因為你mid term溫得足既話，都可能已經熟左3 4成個科。同埋早小小準備，因為有機會mid term一個接一個，中間加埋presetation就真係。 <br />\n每份功課認真對待，考前一兩個星期準備就應該cgpa 3.5以上都無難道，好d既已經上左3.7 甚至爆4。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>Q15到底做功課既groupmates點搵番黎? </strong></span><br />\n有人會係o-day，ocamp，甚至高登搵定未來同學，咁如果咁岩又真係分配到同一個TUTORIAL，就可以有個伴。 <br />\n如果無係開學前準備，第一堂tutorial你都要分組。通常就隨機係你身邊搵d又係單丁既做groupmates。 <br />\n提醒: 如果全部搵同一班人，優點係你地可以夾做邊份野先，大家容易有共息，壞處係一有freeriders，你就科科都比人freeride晒。 <br />\n科科都搵唔同人好處就係無咁易比人freeride，壞處係唔同人面對既DEADLINE係唔同。舉例，依家係８號，你果組既A同學黎緊10號要交一份group project，而你果組已經交左果份group project，所以你想準備一份係14號交既presentation powerpoint。對A黎講，十號果份野就到DEADLINE，你叫佢做份14號交既野緊係睬你都傻啦。就係因為咁，可能你因為無左佢果PART，而做唔到你自己果PART。 <br />\n(補多句，可以既話，最好搵個英文勁人，因為可以幫手睇grammar。)"},{"pid":"d5af4282b0defa3847b02671ee239879e04a8f5c","tid":578360,"uid":165025,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T14:23:25.000Z","msg":"講講讀咩科 <br />\n<br />\n以<span style=\"color: red;\">abagm(general management) </span>為例 <br />\nyear1主要係讀一堆general course同 general education <br />\nyear2 先會讀比較多專注於你果科既野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n參考: <a href=\"http://www.bus.cityu.edu.hk/progABAGM.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bus.cityu.edu.hk%2FprogABAGM.php&d=w%2BnmYi19TIX5nP1VBUj9gr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=08e0253c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bus.cityu.edu.hk/progABAGM.php</a><br />\n<br />\n以<span style=\"color: red;\">econ1</span>為例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n簡單d講 姐係dse微觀經濟+30-40%DSE無教既野eg, 簡單game theory應用<br />\ncourse syllabus 如下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nThe Nature of Economic Problems<br />\nDemand &amp; Supply<br />\nElasticity and its Application<br />\nCosts of Production<br />\nFirms in Competitive Markets<br />\nMonopoly<br />\nMonopolistic Competition<br />\nOligopoly and Game Theory<br />\nExternalities<br />\nMarket Failure and Public Choice<br />\nMarkets for the factors of production<br />\n<br />\n之後講到底一個<span style=\"color: red;\">final grade</span>係點形成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nasso唔同dse <br />\ndse係一試定生死 你果3 4個鍾做得好與唔好就決定左你個grade<br />\n而asso 係有 mid term , presentation , report , 再加exam<br />\n再以 <span style=\"color: red;\">econ1</span>為例<br />\n<br />\nTutorial Presentations : 15%<br />\n同學會係第一堂tutorial 進行分組，之後根據組別次序進行present<br />\necon present 係base on 你做果個topic 再apply番果課既知識去解答D問題<br />\n仲有另一種，例如marketing 同 management , 佢會比一個case你<br />\neg: 759 依家想擴張，你係課堂上學左某個theory 之後要應用佢，再要根據果間公司既實際營環狀況去做 比起econ 或者 financial accounting 依類科既present係煩十倍 所須時間亦多好多<br />\n<br />\nIndividual Report : 10%<br />\n揀份news , 之後用1-2個theory 去解釋現實世界發生既野<br />\n唔難的，老師上堂應該會講解下點做<br />\n(補充，有INDIVIDUAL同時都有GROUP，例如MARRKETING可能會叫你整個產品，之後應用理論去SELL佢，1500字)<br />\n<br />\nMid-term Test :15%<br />\n我果年就測Lecture 1 to Lecture 5.<br />\n30題mc 有認真溫書應該20題左右無問題 拎更多要考下臨場應變能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nfinal exam: 60%<br />\n測晒咁多課<br />\n有mc, sq, lq <br />\nsq,lq 都係有得揀黎答 同tutorial 要你做presentation既題目類似，所以記得係考前做晒佢(所有科都應該咁做) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n注意:每科點評分都可以唔同，有d科有課堂參與分:答問題拎分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>All credit to Reading 巴打#39402 (<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/356259/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/356259/page/1</a>)</ins>"},{"pid":"c89c8818c7d8f539033e44ffb2b7978dbd7829c3","tid":578360,"uid":165025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T14:24:44.000Z","msg":"有個table睇下之前既人升過咩u咩科<br />\n<a href=\"http://bus.cccu.edu.hk/2016/bus_programmes.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbus.cccu.edu.hk%2F2016%2Fbus_programmes.html&d=w%2BnmYi19TIX5nP1VBUj9gr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=993c7f47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bus.cccu.edu.hk/2016/bus_programmes.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇自己TIMETABLE<br />\ntimetable:<br />\n1. 上Cityu aims個網<br />\n2. Log in<br />\n3. Click course registration<br />\n4. Weekly schedule<br />\n<br />\nNotebook ownership program:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hknotebook.com/np17//\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hknotebook.com%2Fnp17%2F%2F&d=w%2BnmYi19TIX5nP1VBUj9gr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=acd89b06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hknotebook.com/np17//</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>All credit to Reading 巴打#39402 (<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/356259/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/356259/page/1</a>)</ins>"},{"pid":"c55e4a951ee36b09d25e1b5770a9a403a45ea61a","tid":578360,"uid":165025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T14:28:22.000Z","msg":"以上全部都係照copy post(3)<br />\n<ins>All credit to Reading 巴打#39402 (<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/356259/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/356259/page/1</a>)</ins> 唔好打我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n估唔到第一個出嘅post就獻左俾cccu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64b9a708af617e058e63e372ace1a1c8d093e4af","tid":578360,"uid":129829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T14:28:37.000Z","msg":"有冇師姐師兄讀韓文加中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗緊下年讀唔讀書好"},{"pid":"728eb1e07040367ae7d3c516c066ddbd3c349229","tid":578360,"uid":101235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T02:57:49.000Z","msg":"有無人讀dss20707 Urban Society and Global Cities, workload係咪好重？ soc sci jj要揀科求意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2910280dc4dcb099a22d99d0d69cd5f9aaab168a","tid":578360,"uid":129042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T04:52:37.000Z","msg":"幾時到2018"},{"pid":"e9c416d76b4370e08a1a426aea4dacc11e78077d","tid":578360,"uid":137233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T11:59:35.000Z","msg":"時光倒流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cf9754555e1ffb71f6e4dd51d28c6716270728e","tid":578360,"uid":4379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T05:50:05.000Z","msg":"想問下如果我喺2018dse雞可以幾時交cccu份申請表？<img src=\"/ass